OL,3,CAt least 90 killed in coal mine gas
OL,4,Cexplosion in China, local media reports
OL,6,FAt least 90 people have been killed in
OL,7,Fa gas explosion at a coal mine in
OL,8,FChina's northern Shanxi province,
OL,9,Flocal media reports.
OL,11,FThe country's official news agency
OL,12,FXinhua said the accident at Changzhi
OL,13,Fcity's Liushenyu coal mine happened on
OL,14,FFriday evening, leaving 247 workers
OL,15,Ftrapped underground.
OL,17,FThe agency initially reported on early
OL,18,FSaturday that eight people were killed
OL,19,Fand 38 were trapped underground.
