OL,3,CAt least 90 killed in coal mine gas
OL,4,Cexplosion in China, local media reports
OL,6,FThe cause is under investigation, and
OL,7,Frescue work is ongoing.
OL,9,FChinese President Xi Jinping has
OL,10,Fcalled for an all-out effort to rescue
OL,11,Fthose missing and to investigate the
OL,12,Fcause of the accident, while holding
OL,13,Fthose responsible accountable,
OL,14,Faccording to Xinhua.
OL,16,FShanxi is China's main coal mining
OL,17,Fprovince.
