OL,3,CAt least 90 killed in coal mine gas
OL,4,Cexplosion in China, local media reports
OL,6,FWith a population of around 34
OL,7,Fmillion, its miners produced 1.3
OL,8,Fbillion tonnes of coal last year,
OL,9,Falmost a third of the country's total.
